INSERT INTO `reviews` VALUES (4,'I bought this for my 2yo to use on long road trips. One of the things I really like about it is that it hooks on to the headrest posts rather than onto the cushion part, which means that it can be used simultaneously with a mirror for her rear facing car seat! We’ve used it for a couple of trips now and it has worked out great. I think the angle would be better if it was used on the back of a seat for a front facing passenger, but it still worked out well enough. It would be nice if the angle was a bit more adjustable than it is. We have an Amazon kids tab and this won’t work with the case on. It isn’t a huge deal yet that we have to take it out because she can’t really reach it to take it out yet, but I can see that being a problem in the future once she can reach. Also, the tablet only fits in horizontally and cannot be used vertically. If you use a cell phone though, that could be (at least mine can. I suppose it depends on how tall your phone is).\r\n','Pretty Good!',4,'2022-11-09 16:59:45.457000',3,5,1),(5,'Very good tablet mount in general. Only issue is full size iPad won’t fit. If you stretch it, you might get it to work assuming no protection sleeves. Personally, I will only use it for iPad mini.','Good mount for smaller tablets',3,'2022-11-09 17:05:42.145000',3,1,1),(6,'I used these 20\'\'20 inserts for 18\'\'18 covers and it worked out great.\r\n\r\nThese will not fluff immediately as soon as they come out of the pack. You will feel disheartened but wait don\'t loose hope and follow the fluffing instructions. You will not regret. they will fluff up magically.\r\n\r\nYou can use the dryer with a tennis ball to fluff them up or you can punch your pillows from all sides and in the middle for some time so that they fluff up. I used both the methods and they fluffed up really well.','Size up to make it look fuller!',4,'2022-11-10 17:07:58.989000',3,16,2),(7,'Summary: This is a review for the black \"Camper\" style Expedition watch with a black Velcro Fast Wrap band. This style is unique from the other Expedition Acadia watches offered by Amazon in that it has water resistance of 100M instead of 50M for the other models. I have seen some non-Amazon reviews showing this same black Timex Expedition watch with 50M water resistance, but mine is 100M. I believe that there is also a white dial version of this watch, too, that is available on Amazon, but it is listed separately from the other Acadia models.','Many Times, the Old-Fashioned, \"Boring\" Ones Make the Best Life Partners',4,'2022-11-16 15:24:29.482000',53,26,0),(8,'I bought this for my husband to replace an older model of the same design that he has been wearing for easily 10 years. The old watchband is a bit the worse for wear, and the glowing watch face doesn\'t work anymore, so I thought he needed an upgrade. He loved his old watch, and so he was very pleased the new one looks the same, feels the same, and has a watch face that actually lights up. I hope Timex keeps offering this style for at least another 30 years, just to keep my husband happy when I decide his old watch is too scruffy for a grown man and want to buy him another.',' Incredibly reliable watch',5,'2022-11-16 15:25:14.678000',53,25,0),(9,'Wanted a simple, casual, analog wrist watch that was sturdy, comfortable, had a light, and especially was easy to read. This watch delivered on all those points. My only gripe is that the second hand tick seems very loud. I find it distracting in quiet settings and when reading. On the other hand, the sound is helpful when counting down the time left in front plank position during core exercises, so there’s the lemonade.','Easy to read, comfortable, but has a loud tick.',5,'2022-11-16 15:25:50.872000',53,23,1),(10,'This watch is comfortable to wear, stylish and takes a beating like a good field watch should. I’ve worn it in the pool and at the water park for extended times For the price I’m thrilled with this watch. As the old slogan says, “takes a lickin’ and keeps on tickin’.”','Excellent weekend watch',4,'2022-11-16 15:26:23.427000',53,27,2),(11,'This a nice watch for the price. I work outside all day and timex has always heald up around my construction work. The band is heavy nylon and should last,\r\nthe only thing that needs improvement is that the band is cut straight across and is sharp. I just took a pair of scissors and nipped the two corners so it would be slightly curved like most watch bands. No big deal. I would still recommend.','Nice watch for the price',5,'2022-11-16 15:26:52.539000',53,21,0),(12,'It\'s a good watch, the strap just seems a bit small. It\'s so light that it feels frail while wearing.','Good watch',4,'2022-11-17 10:54:57.192000',51,27,0),(13,'This watch is superbly designed for it\'s purpose. The black resin case is very tough as is the black nylon strap. The watch is water resistant to 100m/360ft so the watch is effectively waterproof for all water based activities. The large hands and numerals are easy to read at a glance which is ideal for cycling or similar activities when a quick look is all that can be spared. The watch face includes a date window which is also large and clear. The hands are luminous and the watch also has the \'Indiglo\' backlight feature for viewing at night.','A great activity watch.',4,'2022-11-17 10:57:10.888000',51,17,0),(14,'I like walking and climbing, and I work up a bit of a sweat doing so. This did not do my previous, leather-strapped watch any good, and the whole strap fell apart (curiously around the time the battery died). I needed a new watch, quickly. The nylon strap of this time watch appealed, and the muted colour scheme looks smart. It doesn\'t even look that cheap really.',' Basic but neat timepiece',4,'2022-11-17 10:58:02.979000',51,25,0),(15,'A nice little watch at a price the means you don\'t have to worry about bashing it. The 38mm size is misleading as this includes the little protrusions near the crown and on the opposite side. Without these it is only 36mm which suits my 6.75\" wrist. The face is very clear so you can read the time at a glance. The hands have long lasting lume but obviously you have indiglo if it\'s very dark. My watch is loosing 3 seconds a week which is fine at this price point. I noticed that it lost more time if you use the backlight but this could be that the battery needs replacing as it arrived ticking and I no Idea how long it\'s been in storage. Strap is very comfortable and the whole package is as light as a feather. One thing that did impress me was that the second hand hits all the batons on the way round. I\'ve paid more in the past for watches that can\'t manage that. You can sometimes here it ticking but it\'s not at the volume of the Weekender if you are familiar with that model. I\'m very satisfied with this simple low priced watch. Only gripe; Timex, please pull the crown out before dispatch so that the watch arrives with a full battery.','Good every day watch.',4,'2022-11-17 10:58:34.867000',51,6,0),(16,'I am super disappointed with the Timex company regarding this watch. I purchased it as a gift to my aging father in June of 2019. After scarcely 6 months of regular wear, the band fell apart as you can see in the picture. ','Lasted only 6 months! Buyer Beware.',3,'2022-11-17 10:59:14.045000',51,19,0),(17,'I like my Timex Expedition watch because I can wear it daily I like its versatility because the size is quite conservative 40mm in diameter which falls into the category of classic about 9 or 10mm thick which makes it imperceptible on my wrist it is very comfortable and uses a 20mm leather strap this will make my task easier when I want to play with various combinations because it is a standard size and I can find many ( a lot !!)','A great war horse !!!!!!',4,'2022-11-17 10:59:44.162000',51,21,0),(18,'I got this watch to replace a Swiss Army watch that my husband dropped and broke. He doesn\'t like change and I needed something to keep him happy while we work on getting the other one repaired. This looks like the other, it\'s a nice sturdy (sub heavy) watch that appears to be well made and durable. The lighting feature is helpful for those time you DON\'T want your phone to light up the world (and face it, if you are still looking for an indiglo watch, your phone is not your go-to). The band is well made, stitched and appears that it will hold up well.\r\n',' This is a NICE watch!',4,'2022-11-17 11:00:09.177000',51,14,0),(19,'I have several way more experience watches and this is my new ever day watch. Very easy to read looks good and very reliable. Must have','Love this watch',2,'2022-11-17 11:00:43.266000',51,15,0),(20,'The only reason I gave this 4 stars is because his first one stopped working after just a couple of months and he thought it was the battery. After removing the back to replace, found that a part appeared to be defective and because he had removed the back apparently the warranty was negated. Liked it enough to want to get another one and so far so good.',' My husband loves this watch',3,'2022-11-17 11:01:13.677000',51,12,0),(21,'It arrived the next day! It is a gift for my Dad. I have not given the watch to him yet so I am hoping that he likes it. When I rec\'d the watch I thought it was defective bc the second hand was not moving. My bad. I did not realize I had to wind it. The seller would have returned for refund or for exchange it free of charge. No hassles. I am happy with this watch.',' Very nice watch',5,'2022-11-17 11:03:59.488000',51,16,0),(22,'Just got this in the mail so I cannot speak for longevity. But my Husband loved it, it was a Birthday gift. Looks so much nicer than the run of the mill Timex.',' Handsome Watch',2,'2022-11-17 11:04:29.000000',51,7,0),(23,'I bought these my senior year of college and I am so happy that I did. Going to the gym and dealing with the chord from the older iPhone earbuds got pretty annoying. These were super easy just to pop in without dealing with any chords. I also love the ability to double tap to skip a song while in a workout or if I’m not near my phone. I’ve owned these for about a year now and they have never fallen out of my ear unless I accidentally knocked it out by hitting it. The battery life is amazing! One day I realized they were dead, plugged them in before I took the trash out, and they were just about up to 70-75 when I came back. It charges super fast, but the case does die fairly fast when not plugged in. The ease of use for answering phone calls, being alerted for texts, sending texts, accessing Siri, and so much more definitely make this purchase worth it for me. I used these almost every day in college and definitely feel like I got my moneys worth!','Perfect for college!',5,'2022-11-17 11:14:37.553000',50,25,0),(24,'I have been wanting wireless AirPods from Apple for a long time. The price held me back. I tried various other AirPods with little success. These were on sale for $83! So I quickly ordered them as that was the lowest I had seen them for. They are worth every penny!!! I am so happy with them. You just open the case and they pair up with Apple IPhone or IPad. They sound great and they are the first ear pods I have had that actually fit and stay in my ears. The next generation fas extra ear adapting attachments but I didn’t need them. I can hear some outside noise but its not distracting at all. I think the next generation has extra noise canceling built in. But for me, these 2nd generation AirPods are exactly what I was looking for.',' At this price, I could not say no!',5,'2022-11-17 11:15:09.746000',50,23,1),(25,'This product really gives a good first impression.\r\n- No trouble at all connecting like other Bluetooth devices where you kinda have to brace yourself to deal with trouble connecting\r\n- The battery life is great too: you can go for around 2 days without charging.\r\n- But the sound quality wasn’t like ~great. It’s just like the regular EarPods. No bass, no pop, just mediocre sound quality\r\nBut the more you use it, you’ll find more trouble: especially with the auto-connect feature\r\n- I like to watch youtube on my iPad while I’m watching lectures or on a Zoom call.\r\n- And these Air Pods really struggle with, which devices am I gonna connect to.\r\n- It’s kinda annoying to have to manually switch between devices (and it lagged too)\r\n- I think this is kinda short-sighted of Apple since it’s pretty clear that their users are likely to have an ecosystem of Apple products already and like to use them simultaneously.\r\n2nd problem: you don’t know if it’s connected or not','A good but not perfect product',5,'2022-11-17 11:15:55.122000',50,24,0),(26,'Every ear bud I have tried to wiggle and shove in my ears popped right out. That includes a pair of Apple Air pod pros I received as a gift. The only ones that worked were the over the ear type and I could never really find a pair with good sound.\r\nThen the generous person that bought me the pros exchanged them for the Air Pod 3\'s. Like magic they sort of sat in my ears and did not come out!\r\nWhile I liked the 3\'s they became a bit uncomfortable after about 15 minutes or so. A friend suggested the 2s and that was the pair for me. They are smaller than the 3\'s and felt good no matter how long I wore them.','My Choice in 2022!',2,'2022-11-17 11:16:22.108000',50,12,0),(27,'First off, Airpods are great. Seamless connection, great sound quality, compact and high quality design you always receive from apple.',' Best Price Around ',5,'2022-11-17 11:16:57.922000',50,20,0),(28,'Look at the box. If they are A2032, A2031 or A1602, they are Gen2.','CORRECTION: These are gen2',5,'2022-11-17 11:17:22.476000',50,19,0),(29,'Reçu une paire dans une vraie boîte Apple, mais avec des écouteurs qui sont clairement des faux. L\'étui n\'entre pas dans la boîte d\'origine et les écouteurs ne chargent pas. Batterie à 10% après 24h de charge. Plusieurs différences avec des vrais, mais en vérifiant comme il faut. À surveiller!',' Faux Apple à surveiller!',5,'2022-11-17 11:17:45.497000',50,17,0),(30,'If you\'re buying these for on the go, don\'t. If your phone is in your pants pocket they don\'t have a stable connection when outside and there\'s nothing for the bluetooth to bounce off. Pretty useless for walks or commuting on foot.',' Don\'t work outside',3,'2022-11-17 11:18:12.896000',50,21,0),(31,'I have been wanting wireless AirPods from Apple for a long time. The price held me back. I tried various other AirPods with little success. These were on sale for $83! So I quickly ordered them as that was the lowest I had seen them for. They are worth every penny!!! I am so happy with them. You just open the case and they pair up with Apple IPhone or IPad. They sound great and they are the first ear pods I have had that actually fit and stay in my ears. The next generation fas extra ear adapting attachments but I didn’t need them. I can hear some outside noise but its not distracting at all. I think the next generation has extra noise canceling built in. But for me, these 2nd generation AirPods are exactly what I was looking for.',' At this price, I could not say no!',3,'2022-11-17 11:18:49.641000',50,6,0),(32,'Taking the Apple AirPods at face value, they\'re a solid headset for the money! If you already have the original, first generation AirPods and just want to upgrade, not a bad option either. The 2nd generation AirPods feature an improved software chip & runs off of BlueTooth 5.0 vs 4.1 (Gen 1). The software chip allows a faster, stronger, and more stable connection with your device(s). This particular item for $139.00 does NOT feature the wireless charging case. This one must be plugged in via USB (cable provided in the box) to an outlet or USB port. The wireless charging case model is $169. Now if you\'re looking to upgrade to the wireless charging case later on, you can. Apple does sell it separately. If you want the wireless charging option right out of the box, I recommend sending the $169 vs the $139 product here.','100% honest review',4,'2022-11-17 11:19:22.088000',50,22,0),(33,'I just got these ear buds because I was told that I needed some to listen to music at work. It was a standing rule for everyone in the office. I have been using them every day at work and they are great. I discovered that I don\'t have to bring my phone with me if I go across the office to the breakroom, or the rest room. Since I only have one ear bud in at a time, they last pretty much all day.',' Perfect Ear Buds for Work',5,'2022-11-17 11:19:49.257000',50,27,1),(34,'This is the second round of these boots I bought for my kids. They are comfortable for all day at school, like sneakers. Perfect for wet days, feet stay dry and warm. They are not snow boots. We live in Boston and they are not for more than an inch or two of snow. I buy separate true snow boots for ',' Great boots for fall and winter, but too short for deep snow.',4,'2022-11-18 09:33:45.149000',46,28,1),(35,'Perfect gift for God daughter! She loved it as personal n thoughtful momentum special birthday/graduation!','Awesome gift!',5,'2022-11-22 09:08:59.209000',56,30,-1),(36,'Good!','Compact, sturdy',4,'2022-12-01 18:48:38.007000',56,31,-1);
